00:44:30.554 --> 00:44:34.601
We have to believe
that there is a future here.

553
00:44:40.656 --> 00:44:43.726
Kara. where are you?

554
00:44:53.166 --> 00:44:58.426
Honestly. I didn't have a clue that Argo
was different from any other planet.

555
00:45:00.065 --> 00:45:01.826
I thought we were lucky.

556
00:45:03.231 --> 00:45:07.166
But luck. almost by definition.
runs out.

557
00:45:17.155 --> 00:45:18.397
Tell me.

558
00:45:20.335 --> 00:45:22.335
When the city of Argo separated...

559
00:45:22.967 --> 00:45:27.389
...it unearthed a crystalline
mineral from deep within the planet

560
00:45:28.764 --> 00:45:29.810
Kryptonite

561
00:45:30.747 --> 00:45:33.075
The ground is poisoned.

562
00:45:33.676 --> 00:45:36.169
It made all the people of Argo sick...

563
00:45:36.614 --> 00:45:39.106
...and it is spreading.

564
00:45:40.786 --> 00:45:43.301
Can we do something?

565
00:46:14.776 --> 00:46:16.698
The radiation took hold of me as well.

566
00:46:17.135 --> 00:46:19.346
I won't let it reach you.

567
00:46:22.706 --> 00:46:26.003
I found my brother's
sketches for the escape pod.

568
00:46:27.267 --> 00:46:29.009
I built one for you

569
00:46:29.783 --> 00:46:31.876
You will follow your cousin. Kal-El.

570
00:46:33.470 --> 00:46:36.431
You will have a new home on Earth.

571
00:46:39.753 --> 00:46:40.745
No

572
00:46:42.198 --> 00:46:43.800
This is my home.

573
00:46:44.425 --> 00:46:46.737
It is my only home.

574
00:46:50.433 --> 00:46:52.433
Let the radiation reach me.

575
00:46:54.080 --> 00:46:58.174
I will lie on the ground
next to you and mom.

576
00:47:01.565 --> 00:47:03.565
I am only one small life.

577
00:47:04.565 --> 00:47:08.565
What difference does
it make if I live or die?

578
00:47:09.475 --> 00:47:11.475
You are not just one small life.

579
00:47:12.928 --> 00:47:15.428
You are your mother's life.

580
00:47:17.318 --> 00:47:19.318
You are my life.

581
00:47:20.115 --> 00:47:23.725
You are our souls
unfolding into the future.

582
00:47:25.207 --> 00:47:26.355
My daughter...

583
00:47:26.847 --> 00:47:29.597
...this is the reason for your existence.

584
00:47:42.677 --> 00:47:44.497
When I am gone...

585
00:47:45.740 --> 00:47:49.029
...promise me something.

586
00:47:50.208 --> 00:47:51.661
Of course. mother.

587
00:47:54.442 --> 00:47:55.544
Be good.

588
00:47:55.708 --> 00:47:59.840
That does not mean you are weak.

589
00:48:00.231 --> 00:48:03.294
Nor that you are kind.

590
00:48:05.855 --> 00:48:07.785
But you must be good.

591
00:48:16.716 --> 00:48:18.990
We do not choose our path

592
00:48:21.419 --> 00:48:24.153
Your path will be one of great effort...

593
00:48:26.427 --> 00:48:28.427
...and of great purpose.

594
00:48:30.419 --> 00:48:35.708
Wherever you are going.
you will have great power.

595
00:48:37.393 --> 00:48:38.753
Use it to protect those...

596
00:48:39.050 --> 00:48:41.050
...who cannot protect themselves.

597
00:48:42.721 --> 00:48:44.721
Trust yourself...

598
00:48:45.120 --> 00:48:46.800
...in knowing what is right.

599
00:49:28.472 --> 00:49:30.097
We are with you.

600
00:50:04.066 --> 00:50:05.066
So yeah.

601
00:50:08.416 --> 00:50:11.926
When I say I know what it's like.
I'm not talking out of my ass. Ruthye.

602
00:50:12.071 --> 00:50:13.506
Grief is a killer. you know?

603
00:50:13.646 --> 00:50:15.606
It can make you want to break bad or...

604
00:50:16.806 --> 00:50:18.286
you know. get revenge. but...

605
00:50:22.036 --> 00:50:25.196
I don't think any of those things are
going to lead you to where you want to go.

606
00:50:28.736 --> 00:50:29.736
So what does?

607
00:50:31.826 --> 00:50:33.106
When did you stop feeling angry?

608
00:50:35.756 --> 00:50:36.756
Any day now.

609
00:50:53.969 --> 00:50:56.786
Um. I'm just going to go check on him.

610
00:50:57.516 --> 00:50:58.516
Stay here.

611
00:51:28.816 --> 00:51:29.876
Where's your friend?

612
00:51:30.666 --> 00:51:31.666
They come now.

613
00:51:31.756 --> 00:51:32.756
Sit.

614
00:51:46.523 --> 00:51:50.643
Recipe from my mother.
from her mother.etc...

615
00:51:53.016 --> 00:51:54.396
A little bitter.

616
00:51:54.676 --> 00:51:55.676
Thank you.

617
00:51:56.316 --> 00:51:57.316
Drink.

618
00:52:09.116 --> 00:52:10.676
How does your friend know the brigands?

619
00:52:13.056 --> 00:52:15.276
We all know the brigands.

620
00:52:18.386 --> 00:52:19.036
But you said...

621
00:52:19.136 --> 00:52:21.496
Brigands come here. take girls.

622
00:52:22.416 --> 00:52:25.156
They come here to take our girl.

623
00:52:27.796 --> 00:52:28.796
Zarna.

624
00:52:30.716 --> 00:52:35.416
Yeah. your. um. your daughter.
the... the pictures.

625
00:52:38.556 --> 00:52:39.556
What did you give me?

626
00:52:40.736 --> 00:52:41.736
Sorry. sorry.

627
00:52:41.776 --> 00:52:42.376
Stop drinking.

628
00:52:42.643 --> 00:52:43.643
Stop drinking.

629
00:52:43.795 --> 00:52:45.795
Bomar. stop! She is our
daughter. we have no choice.

630
00:52:45.896 --> 00:52:48.396
Did you get this poison from the brigands?

631
00:52:48.636 --> 00:52:49.636
I don't understand.

632
00:52:50.369 --> 00:52:51.490
You should be...

633
00:52:51.818 --> 00:52:52.871
...paralyzed.

634
00:52:53.536 --> 00:52:55.036
This is just really going to suck.

635
00:53:06.796 --> 00:53:07.272
Milk

636
00:53:07.296 --> 00:53:07.696
Why?

637
00:53:07.697 --> 00:53:11.156
Well. it coats your stomach if you've been
poisoned.

638
00:53:11.621 --> 00:53:12.621
Come on. man.

639
00:53:12.668 --> 00:53:13.748
It's a white liquid.

640
00:53:13.856 --> 00:53:15.156
Help me out of here.

641
00:53:24.126 --> 00:53:25.766
What kind of milk is that?

642
00:53:26.026 --> 00:53:27.026
Chu-Kan

643
00:53:27.466 --> 00:53:28.466
Chu-Kan

644
00:53:28.921 --> 00:53:29.766
Oh. my God.

645
00:53:29.846 --> 00:53:30.846
Okay.

646
00:53:31.476 --> 00:53:32.766
So you sold me out for what?

647
00:53:32.886 --> 00:53:34.326
What are you getting in return?

648
00:53:35.606 --> 00:53:36.606
Speak.

649
00:53:37.133 --> 00:53:39.373
One girl for two girls.

650
00:54:12.296 --> 00:54:13.336
Hello

651
00:54:17.036 --> 00:54:18.156
Are you okay?

652
00:54:21.646 --> 00:54:23.826
I heard you were looking for me.

653
00:54:29.496 --> 00:54:31.196
Technically. you found me.

654
00:54:58.556 --> 00:55:01.216
Hey man. can you just give me one second?

655
00:55:12.563 --> 00:55:14.563
Thanks...i needed that.

656
00:55:30.026 --> 00:55:33.466
You dropped your puppy's ante-tongue.

657
00:55:38.552 --> 00:55:39.310
Kara !

658
00:55:42.052 --> 00:55:43.279
Help me !

659
00:55:50.007 --> 00:55:50.820
Stop !

660
00:55:52.843 --> 00:55:53.867
Kara !!!

661
00:56:14.611 --> 00:56:15.416
Sorry

662
00:56:18.096 --> 00:56:19.116
Are you drunk?

663
00:56:19.276 --> 00:56:20.276
No!

664
00:56:26.186 --> 00:56:29.126
Hey. she don't look very poisoned to me.
eh?

665
00:56:30.981 --> 00:56:32.099
Bring me their daughter.

666
00:56:32.192 --> 00:56:32.873
Now.

667
00:56:33.296 --> 00:56:34.606
You smell of vomit?

668
00:56:34.607 --> 00:56:35.927
It's because Mareck poisoned me.

669
00:56:37.351 --> 00:56:39.066
Oh. and I am fine. thank you for asking.

670
00:57:07.147 --> 00:57:08.663
The brides !

671
00:57:08.944 --> 00:57:09.936
Catch them!

672
00:57:14.156 --> 00:57:15.156
Don't move.

673
00:57:48.129 --> 00:57:48.691
Run !

674
00:58:01.796 --> 00:58:05.916
Drom Baxton. there's a lot of rich
dipshits looking for you.

675
00:58:06.056 --> 00:58:07.076
Screw you. old man.

676
00:58:10.396 --> 00:58:11.396
Shit.

677
00:58:26.169 --> 00:58:27.896
A deal's a deal.

678
00:58:28.654 --> 00:58:29.888
She must die.

679
00:58:49.948 --> 00:58:50.948
Ouch.

680
00:58:58.696 --> 00:59:00.656
Aren't you the dips from that diet bar?

681
00:59:00.816 --> 00:59:01.816
Funny.

682
00:59:02.296 --> 00:59:03.656
That's what I've been calling you.

683
00:59:03.916 --> 00:59:04.916
Touche.

684
01:00:08.746 --> 01:00:10.126
Oh. that's ballsy.

685
01:00:10.726 --> 01:00:11.726
Drom Baxton !

686
01:00:11.806 --> 01:00:13.126
You just made me angry.

687
01:00:23.466 --> 01:00:24.466
Got ya. bastards!

688
01:00:34.461 --> 01:00:36.078
Sarna !

689
01:00:37.808 --> 01:00:39.204
Where are you?

690
01:00:39.783 --> 01:00:40.416
You okay?

691
01:00:40.696 --> 01:00:41.176
Yeah?

692
01:00:41.376 --> 01:00:42.516
Okay. get her out of here.

693
01:00:42.736 --> 01:00:43.596
She's the last one.

694
01:00:43.676 --> 01:00:43.816
Go!

695
01:00:44.036 --> 01:00:45.036
Go!

696
01:00:58.816 --> 01:01:00.096
Come on. Krem.

697
01:01:00.356 --> 01:01:01.656
Where's my antidote?

698
01:01:02.256 --> 01:01:04.656
You like to play games.

699
01:01:05.966 --> 01:01:07.396
I can play games.

700
01:01:14.056 --> 01:01:16.076
I can smell you.

701
01:01:35.356 --> 01:01:36.996
I told you not to move!

702
01:01:37.096 --> 01:01:37.616
I had him!

703
01:01:37.856 --> 01:01:38.856
Hide.

704
01:01:44.591 --> 01:01:45.544
Shit

705
01:01:48.006 --> 01:01:49.006
Sarna!

706
01:01:54.586 --> 01:01:54.986
No!

707
01:01:54.987 --> 01:01:55.987
No!

708
01:01:56.846 --> 01:01:57.846
Stop!

709
01:02:28.956 --> 01:02:29.716
They're dead!

710
01:02:29.836 --> 01:02:31.956
Because you did not let me do what had to
be done!

711
01:02:32.416 --> 01:02:34.192
Okay. Ruthye. I'm not letting you kill
that man.

712
01:02:34.216 --> 01:02:35.216
Why not?

713
01:02:35.356 --> 01:02:37.076
Look at the suffering he leaves in his
wake!

714
01:02:37.176 --> 01:02:37.976
Why does he get to be alive?

715
01:02:38.146 --> 01:02:39.876
Okay. okay. stop freaking out!

716
01:02:40.116 --> 01:02:41.116
Get off!

717
01:02:41.426 --> 01:02:43.196
Don't tell me not to freak out!

718
01:02:43.976 --> 01:02:44.976
I'm allowed.

719
01:02:45.696 --> 01:02:46.696
Tell me why.

720
01:02:46.906 --> 01:02:48.026
Because it will mess you up.

721
01:02:48.646 --> 01:02:50.236
You think it'll make you feel better?

722
01:02:50.336 --> 01:02:51.336
It won't!

723
01:02:51.686 --> 01:02:53.416
It'll haunt you for the rest of your life!

724
01:02:53.756 --> 01:02:54.756
Is that what you want?

725
01:02:57.036 --> 01:02:58.516
So the alternative is to be like you?

726
01:02:59.576 --> 01:03:00.576
Constantly...

727
01:03:00.616 --> 01:03:02.656
Leaving your planet to drink yourself into
a stupor?

728
01:03:03.486 --> 01:03:05.956
Drunk all of the time so you never have to
feel anything?

729
01:03:06.116 --> 01:03:06.616
Guess what?

730
01:03:07.136 --> 01:03:08.796
I. too. want to free myself of this pain.

731
01:03:09.566 --> 01:03:10.886
And I do not want to be like you.

732
01:03:12.016 --> 01:03:13.016
Okay.

733
01:03:14.456 --> 01:03:16.398
Then why don't you go
find whatever dimensional

734
01:03:16.422 --> 01:03:18.780
portal he just passed
through all by yourself?

735
01:04:38.936 --> 01:04:39.416
Hey!

736
01:04:39.417 --> 01:04:39.896
Squidward!

737
01:04:40.016 --> 01:04:41.016
Where are the brigands?

738
01:04:41.156 --> 01:04:42.156
No idea.

739
01:04:42.196 --> 01:04:43.196
Really?

740
01:04:44.156 --> 01:04:44.636
Bullshit.

741
01:04:44.796 --> 01:04:47.116
I have less than 24 hours to save my dog.

742
01:04:47.696 --> 01:04:50.736
So you tell me where the brigands are and
I won't  turn you into a hand puppet.

743
01:04:51.156 --> 01:04:51.636
Okay?

744
01:04:52.836 --> 01:04:53.836
Okay.

745
01:04:57.955 --> 01:04:58.401
OK

746
01:04:59.386 --> 01:05:00.466
We will have to wear these.

747
01:05:06.956 --> 01:05:07.956
Let's go.

748
01:05:42.320 --> 01:05:44.276
This is as close as we get.

749
01:06:29.676 --> 01:06:32.512
PLANET: BARENTON
SOLAR CATEGORY: GREEN AND YELLOW

750
01:06:53.106 --> 01:06:54.106
Hi there.

751
01:06:57.246 --> 01:06:59.126
I've been tracking your ship for the last
month.

752
01:06:59.216 --> 01:07:00.666
I believe you're from Krypton?

753
01:07:01.066 --> 01:07:02.126
And so am I.

754
01:07:03.886 --> 01:07:04.886
Clark.

755
01:07:06.550 --> 01:07:07.885
I don't understand what you are saying.

756
01:07:08.815 --> 01:07:10.346
Where am i?

757
01:07:10.800 --> 01:07:12.800
I am on Earth?

758
01:07:13.518 --> 01:07:14.756
Are you Kal-El?

759
01:07:14.976 --> 01:07:16.046
Oh. I'm sorry.

760
01:07:16.166 --> 01:07:17.466
I don't... Oh. I don't...

761
01:07:17.566 --> 01:07:20.066
I don't speak Kryptonian.

762
01:07:20.086 --> 01:07:22.206
I never....shoot.

763
01:07:23.326 --> 01:07:25.716
I... I wasn't raised there.
so... I wasn't raised there.

764
01:07:25.806 --> 01:07:26.806
Why am I talking louder?

765
01:07:26.866 --> 01:07:27.866
Uh. let me help you.

766
01:07:28.440 --> 01:07:30.261
Krypto. behave yourself.

767
01:07:31.011 --> 01:07:31.570
Be good.

768
01:07:31.876 --> 01:07:32.876
It's a feisty little guy.

769
01:07:33.666 --> 01:07:34.666
He's cute.

770
01:07:36.126 --> 01:07:37.126
Is it okay if I...

771
01:07:41.626 --> 01:07:43.166
Watch your step there.

772
01:07:44.606 --> 01:07:45.626
Might be slippery. so...

773
01:07:46.176 --> 01:07:46.986
Is this. um...

774
01:07:47.086 --> 01:07:48.086
I'll grab it.

775
01:07:49.526 --> 01:07:50.526
Okay.

776
01:07:51.726 --> 01:07:52.726
Ah. yeah.

777
01:07:52.926 --> 01:07:53.926
Pretty cool. huh?

778
01:07:56.006 --> 01:07:56.546
Don't worry.

779
01:07:56.626 --> 01:07:57.746
We don't actually live here.

780
01:07:58.676 --> 01:08:00.596
There's a lot more to Earth than just this
place.

781
01:08:01.626 --> 01:08:02.626
Big city.

782
01:08:03.001 --> 01:08:04.001
Lots of stuff to do.

783
01:08:04.466 --> 01:08:04.866
Bowling.

784
01:08:05.006 --> 01:08:06.006
That's fun.

785
01:08:06.146 --> 01:08:07.586
Uh. it was a big adjustment for me.

786
01:08:07.926 --> 01:08:09.022
You know. coming from Kansas.

787
01:08:09.046 --> 01:08:12.127
You know. I'm a small-town kind
of guy. but. uh... You know Kansas?

788
01:08:12.526 --> 01:08:12.926
No.

789
01:08:13.066 --> 01:08:14.106
Why would you know Kansas?

790
01:08:14.206 --> 01:08:15.206
What am I...

791
01:08:16.956 --> 01:08:19.076
You can't understand a word that I'm
saying right now.

792
01:08:20.786 --> 01:08:21.786
It's okay.

793
01:08:22.086 --> 01:08:22.646
It's okay.

794
01:08:22.647 --> 01:08:23.647
You will one day.

795
01:08:24.036 --> 01:08:26.786
And you'll also learn to love this place.
just like I have.

796
01:08:27.926 --> 01:08:28.926
Promise.

797
01:08:32.970 --> 01:08:34.422
Why is he in his underwear?

798
01:08:34.618 --> 01:08:36.418
Oh. I should mention...

799
01:08:38.576 --> 01:08:42.866
Your powers are gonna start
kicking in... right about... now.

800
01:08:57.930 --> 01:08:59.766
How can this be my home?

801
01:10:06.456 --> 01:10:07.976
I thought that the shelter might help.

802
01:10:08.256 --> 01:10:09.256
Was I right?

803
01:10:09.796 --> 01:10:12.696
What did you...

804
01:10:12.946 --> 01:10:15.836
I saw you boarding that man's ship.
so I snuck up into the cargo hold.

805
01:10:16.916 --> 01:10:17.916
What's this place?

806
01:10:22.256 --> 01:10:23.256
It's my prison.

807
01:10:24.671 --> 01:10:27.566
I'm afraid it's now that the planet orbits
between...

808
01:10:28.616 --> 01:10:29.616
two suns.

809
01:10:31.528 --> 01:10:32.898
And that the green sun...

810
01:10:34.046 --> 01:10:35.126
can kill me.

811
01:10:39.421 --> 01:10:40.581
Krem left your ship on Bilquis.

812
01:10:41.076 --> 01:10:42.076
And I found this.

813
01:10:44.256 --> 01:10:45.416
I thought that it might help.

814
01:10:49.161 --> 01:10:51.706
It's just a stupid suit. Ruthye.

815
01:10:55.036 --> 01:10:56.036
It doesn't do anything.

816
01:11:08.173 --> 01:11:09.189
My dog...

817
01:11:15.355 --> 01:11:16.355
...my Krypto...

818
01:11:18.656 --> 01:11:19.816
I'm not there to say goodbye.

819
01:11:22.296 --> 01:11:23.687
I just want...

820
01:11:24.121 --> 01:11:25.481
Hey. Kara...

821
01:11:27.481 --> 01:11:28.551
...don't freak out.

822
01:11:40.176 --> 01:11:42.506
I'm so sorry for saying I didn't want to
be like you.

823
01:11:47.266 --> 01:11:51.926
I mean. you're not always nice.
but you're kind.

824
01:11:54.736 --> 01:11:56.576
And you're not always perfect.
but you're good.

825
01:12:02.126 --> 01:12:03.586
So thank you for taking me with you.

826
01:12:19.113 --> 01:12:20.674
Water...

827
01:14:06.411 --> 01:14:07.599
Gotcha

828
01:14:12.066 --> 01:14:13.066
Thank you.

829
01:14:14.646 --> 01:14:15.346
I guess.

830
